data.description: Don't miss this great opportunity! 2 Bedroom / 2 Bathroom / 2 Car Garage Single Family Home Located In Beacon Woods. Enjoy Conservation View In Front of the Home. Low HOA of $72/ Quarter and No CDD fees! As you step through Double Door Entry, you are greeted by the formal living and dining room. Split Bedroom Floorplan. Kitchen with Full Appliance Package, Pantry and Pass-Thru Window. Owner’s Retreat w/ Walk-In Closet and Sliders leading to Florida Room and Screened In Lanai. Cedar-Lined Closet in Secondary Bedroom. New Ductwork and AC in 2017. Community amenities include clubhouse, heated pool, tennis courts, basketball courts, bocce courts, playground, and picnic areas. Close to area beaches, public boat ramp to Gulf of Mexico, shopping and restaurants!! Schedule your showing today!
